none: Locations of requests, complaints and reports about lighting in 1925

Around 1921, Melbourne printers Anderson, Gowan produced a series of maps of metropolitan municipalities. We've annotated this contemporary map with the locations mentioned under "Lamps and Lighting" in the Town Clerk's subject index.
"Municipality of Melbourne," (Melbourne: Anderson, Gowan, c. 1921), State Library of Victoria, http://handle.slv.vic.gov.au/10381/166007.
